Class LinkElement

    • io.reinert.requestor.core.header.Element

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Link

    public class LinkElement
extends Element.SimpleElement
implements Link

    Link header element.

    It parses a single link value from a link header and fills the Link properties accordingly.

    Author:
    Danilo Reinert
